name: Airforce uniform
description:
This model was made as a test, so it may not be that good.

Put (service cap, flight cap) in negative prompt if you do not want the cap.

If you have any ideas for LoRA's let me know.

All images were made with High-Res-Fix and 4x-UltraSharp, some were made with Dynamic Thresholding.

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description:
airforce_uniform is the activation word

  • Removed image that was causing weird glowing effect

  • Backgrounds should be a little more flexible

  • Played around with the captions

  • Added service cap and flight cap, flight cap does not work seems to get overwritten by the service cap
